-- Indonesia to Release 500,000 Tons of Rice to Cool Prices, Kontan Reports
-- Yoga Rusmana
-- 2010-08-03T00:26:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-03/indonesia-to-release-500-000-tons-of-rice-to-cool-prices-kontan-reports.html

          
          
             Indonesia will start selling 500,000
metric tons of rice at below market prices this month to help
cool food inflation and ensure that the staple remains
affordable, Kontan reported, citing Deputy Agriculture Minister
Bayu Krisnamurthi.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
